      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "見つかりません"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No repositories registered": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "リポジトリが未登録です"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No session selected": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッション未選択"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Notification Hooks": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通知フック"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Notification: %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "通知: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open config.json…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "config.json を開く…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Operation Failed": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "操作に失敗しました"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Placeholders: {project} (repository name), {branch} (/ normalized to -), {branch_raw} (as is). The hook receives VITERM_WORKTREE_PATH / VITERM_BRANCH / VITERM_GIT_ROOT.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "プレースホルダ: {project}(リポジトリ名)、{branch}(/ は - に正規化)、{branch_raw}(そのまま)。フックには VITERM_WORKTREE_PATH / VITERM_BRANCH / VITERM_GIT_ROOT が渡されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Post-Creation Hook:": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "作成後フック:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Press ⌘T to start a session or ⌘N to create a worktree": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "⌘T でセッションを起動 / ⌘N で worktree を作成"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Registered Repositories:": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "登録リポジトリ:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Remove": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "削除"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rename": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "リネーム"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rename Session": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッションをリネーム"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Rename…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "リネーム…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Repositories": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "リポジトリ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Runs via /bin/sh -c when a session state changes (leave empty to disable). Environment variables: VITERM_SESSION_NAME / VITERM_WORKTREE_PATH / VITERM_OLD_STATE / VITERM_NEW_STATE. Example: play a sound on waiting for input → afplay /System/Library/Sounds/Glass.aiff": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッション状態の変化時に /bin/sh -c で実行されます(空で無効)。環境変数: VITERM_SESSION_NAME / VITERM_WORKTREE_PATH / VITERM_OLD_STATE / VITERM_NEW_STATE。例: 入力待ちで音を鳴らす → afplay /System/Library/Sounds/Glass.aiff"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Search commands…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "コマンドを検索…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Select the root directory of a git repository": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "git リポジトリのルートディレクトリを選択"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Session": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッション"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Session %lld": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッション %lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Settings…": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "設定…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Show in Finder": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Finder で表示"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Some steps failed: %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "一部のステップが失敗: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Split Down": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "下に分割"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Split Right": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "右に分割"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Terminate": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "終了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Terminate Session": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "セッションを終了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The default preset is used for ⌘T, “＋ Add Session”, and the session launched when creating a worktree. Presets themselves are edited in the presets section of config.json.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "既定プリセットは ⌘T・「＋ セッションを追加」・worktree 作成時のセッション起動に使われます。プリセットの定義自体は config.json の presets で編集します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The destination path collides with an existing worktree": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "作成先パスが既存の worktree と衝突しています"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The running process will be terminated and the scrollback will be discarded.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "実行中のプロセスは終了され、スクロールバックも破棄されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This will delete %@ (%@).": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%1$@(%2$@)を削除します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Toggle Sidebar": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "サイドバー表示切替"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Waiting for input: %@": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "入力待ち: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When busy:": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "busy になったとき:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When idle:": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "idle になったとき:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When waiting for input:": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "入力待ちになったとき:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "e.g. npm install (leave empty to disable)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "npm install など(空で無効)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "viterm Settings": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "viterm 設定"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "~/repo, ~/work (comma-separated, leave empty to disable)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "~/repo, ~/work(カンマ区切り、空で無効)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "⌘⇧U jump to waiting": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "⌘⇧U 未読へ"
          }
